     so ATO 2.6 filmstrip always has access to all 3 stages.
  4. UMAP fallback checks file existence before display (no crash on clean run).
  5. PNG static fallbacks removed from sandbox/evolution/t-SNE cells; plots
     are generated inline by matplotlib (always available).
